---
title: Soy-Glazed Chicken & Scallion Broccoli Cashew Rice, Spicy Mayo & Lime
description: Prep, sizzle, zap, serve—that’s the sound of this weeknight wonder meal! Thanks to a few clever time-savers from our chefs, you’ll be savoring a buttery cashew-lime rice topped with saucy soy-glazed chicken and garlicky steamed broccoli with scallions and chili flakes in just 15 minutes—no joke! Drizzle your bowls with creamy spicy mayo, sprinkle with scallion greens and crispy fried onions, then finish with a bright squeeze of fresh lime juice for a deliciously balanced bowl (fast!).
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6643638438584bf020f8c6c4-e9ad27c9.jpeg
